Starter Project: #9 TV B Gone
Main Project: #110 Voice Controlled Robot


Major Steps to complete the project:
1. Material Acquisition 
	
2. The H-Bridge L293D
Connect motors to H-Bridge

3. Moving the Robot Around
Coding for movement. Make sure the code works

4. Connect NodeMCU to WiFi 
Download code from github

5. Finish code 
Integrate code with the robot. Use personal hotspot.


6. Develop android app 
Code basic functions
Make buttons 
Voice recognition

7. Assembling Robot Body
 

Potential Modifications:
1. Blow it up

